US DOT (Department of Transportation)

1. World Area Code table:
1.1. Go to http://www.transtats.bts.gov/DL_SelectFields.asp?Table_ID=315&DB_Short_Name=Aviation%20Support%20Tables
1.2. Select all the fields
1.3. Download the file. The file name should be something like 495998804_T_WAC_COUNTRY_STATE.zip
1.4. Extract the compressed file

2. Area codes for every airport:
http://www.dot.gov/sites/dot.dev/files/docs/airports_codes.txt

